query:
INSERT INTO BestProRecords (
                       filter_id,
                       player_id,
                       record_id,
                       points,
                       time
                     )
                     VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?, ?)
                     ON DUPLICATE KEY
                     UPDATE record_id = VALUES(record_id),
                            points = VALUES(points),
                            time = VALUES(time)
